{"tid":1769832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"棒球全球五十大最具影響力人物 香港示威者及前線戰士上榜","createTime":"2019-12-05T07:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T00:31:43.000Z","uid":110611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"849f773b324a6fc969a522cf403f3482b5af1930","tid":1769832,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"Source 蘋果"},{"pid":"0d1a0611f90d1f4285997e2fca30a77ed4508015","tid":1769832,"uid":110611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191205&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60344800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191205%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60344800&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1exjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=12953a5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191205%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60344800&h=93fe5ea7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191205&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60344800</a><br />\n<br />\n美國彭博新聞網站選出全球50大最具影響力人物，「香港示威者及前線戰士」（Hong Kong Protesters, the Frontline Fighters）上榜。<br />\n<br />\n彭博新聞網站解釋時，以「香港示威者及前線戰士」為題，配以身穿黑衣、戴著黃色頭盔、眼罩、面罩的勇武示威者相片。報道形容，港人的抗爭已持續6個月，高峰期涉及200萬人，始於港府強推《逃犯條例》修訂，觸發市民對中國司法制度不透明的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n報道形容，這場運動無大台、無領袖，全靠網上討論區動員，開始時主要是和平集會及示威，起初民眾只是以雨傘抵擋催淚彈。雖然政府最終撤回條例，但示威者仍堅持尋求真普選等民主訴求，持續的動盪更不惜令香港經濟付上代價。而香港政府及北京高官在香港局勢升級之時，一直寸步不讓，最終在區議會選舉中，泛民取得壓倒性勝利，同時美國總統特朗普亦簽署《香港人權及民主法案》，表達對香港示威者的支持。"},{"pid":"039e1c6e9c6a88a4fec8cb7f60899dc454869dc9","tid":1769832,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/1200x800/public/d8/images/methode/2019/10/04/684fae66-e5cb-11e9-8a10-b9721f28293e_image_hires_110202.JPG?itok=VG894iB8&amp;v=1570158127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F1200x800%2Fpublic%2Fd8%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F684fae66-e5cb-11e9-8a10-b9721f28293e_image_hires_110202.JPG%3Fitok%3DVG894iB8%26v%3D1570158127&h=eb9590f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.dimsumdaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06080539/Screenshot-2019-09-06-at-8.04.29-AM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.dimsumdaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F06080539%2FScreenshot-2019-09-06-at-8.04.29-AM1.jpg&h=eda071d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ede701b1389fea776c99d9abf337bee1c4d934b","tid":1769832,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd2a73e7ba7ec4d44dee1bb60bd7fee9c7977a2c","tid":1769832,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"等睇上埋time<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9ca380bfe0ec53957eee362711f2ae446220e1","tid":1769832,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一生人上一次times<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2c11296bd1f9adfe228dd61f61f3babb559ec5be","tid":1769832,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"好似陣係前線 應該係「香港示威者&mdash;前線」"},{"pid":"6b9bb9e69523e28c1db03396ceca3a9ed7a324d9","tid":1769832,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"11759f2535ff225b4ac452b1b9c700f005dfc091","tid":1769832,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d1a0611f90d1f4285997e2fca30a77ed4508015","tid":1769832,"uid"